Salad Dressings

### Ranch

- 1/2 cup mayo
- 1/2 cup plain full-fat greek yogurt
- 1/2 cup cream
- 2 tbsp lemon juice or white vinegar
- worcestershire sauce
- garlic
- chives
- dill
- black pepper
- salt
- parsley
- onion/shallots

Herbs can be dried or fresh.

### Green Goddess

- 1 cup mayo
- 3/4 cup sour cream
- 1/3 cup chopped fresh parsley
- 1/3 cup chopped fresh tarragon
- 1/3 cup chopped fresh chives
- 2 tbsp lemon juice
- 1 tbsp rice vinegar
- 1 anchovy fillet
- 1 clove garlic, minced
- salt, pepper, and cayenne to taste

### Ginger Tahini

- 1 cup garlic, peanut, or olive oil
- 1/3 cup tahini
- 2 tbsp grated ginger
- 3 cloves minced garlic
- 1 tbsp miso paste
- 1 tbsp rice vinegar
- 1 tbsp soy sauce
- 1 tsp sesame oil
- sugar and salt to taste
- water to thin
